SELECT viz7.c1239tyc_main.TYC AS "object_name" , round(((viz7.c1239tyc_main.Vmag/1000.0))::numeric,2) AS "V" , round(((viz7.c1239tyc_main.B_V/1000.0))::numeric,3)+round(((viz7.c1239tyc_main.Vmag/1000.0))::numeric,2) AS "B" , round(((viz7.c1239tyc_main.B_V/1000.0))::numeric,3) AS "B-V" , viz7.c1239tyc_main.RAhms AS "RA" , viz7.c1239tyc_main.DEdms AS "DE"
FROM viz7.c1239tyc_main
WHERE viz7.c1239tyc_main.TYC = '1266  1416 1'
Limit 100
